B.Dp=s(["When you feel like you cannot do it anymore, just remember: 'Allah does not burden a soul beyond that it can bear.' (Quran 2:286)","Salah is not a burden; it is a remedy for the weary soul.","If you want to talk to Allah, pray. If you want Allah to talk to you, read the Quran.","Sujood is the beautiful connection between you and your Creator; the closer your head is to the ground, the closer your heart is to Allah.","Don't rush your prayer; you are standing in front of the Master of the universe.","A life without prayer is a life without peace.","The golden time for Fajr changes your entire day's barakah (blessings).","No matter how far you've gone, the door to repentance is always open; just turn back in Salah.","Whenever you feel alone, remember Allah is closer to you than your jugular vein.","Prayer is the first thing you will be asked about on the Day of Judgment; make sure it is perfect."],t.s)
